944
00:41:53,244 --> 00:41:55,194
but I never would have
pushed you towards him

945
00:41:55,263 --> 00:41:57,247
if I thought that
you'd end up hurt.

946
00:41:57,315 --> 00:41:59,349
I didn't see it coming.

947
00:41:59,417 --> 00:42:02,418
You did, and I am so sorry.

948
00:42:02,487 --> 00:42:04,720
But it was one crappy call.

949
00:42:04,789 --> 00:42:06,121
That's all.

950
00:42:06,190 --> 00:42:07,556
<i>So what'll it be?</i>

951
00:42:08,793 --> 00:42:10,326
<i>Trick?</i>

952
00:42:11,829 --> 00:42:13,579
<i>Or treat?</i>

953
00:42:13,648 --> 00:42:17,048
Get in, before the
trick-or-treaters think that I'm home.
